title: Ebro In The Morning - Flo Rida Appreciation Day + NYC Public Advocate Jumaane Williams
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/28. 

WOULD YOU EVER LICK THE STACHE? (1:46:20) NYC Public Advocate - Jumaane Williams stops by the program (27). Ebro and the crew give away Summer Jam tickets, Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12, 1:08 & 1:49), and you find out who played themselves (18:30).  

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
